channel.title: I can't join server, others can?
channel.description:
Hello guys...
In my CMD there are people joining my server.... And when I go into the character log there are players in there who are logged onto my server !!
The thing is I cannot get onto my server... It's defiantly up as there is information comming through the CMD !!
Help??
Thanks!
